variables.name: deviceAddress
variables.comment: * The device MAC address uniquely identifies a Wi-Fi p2p device

variables.name: GROUP_OWNER_BAND_AUTO
variables.comment: * Allow the system to pick the operating frequency from all supported bands.

variables.name: GROUP_OWNER_BAND_2GHZ
variables.comment: * Allow the system to pick the operating frequency from the 2.4 GHz band.

variables.name: GROUP_OWNER_BAND_5GHZ
variables.comment: * Allow the system to pick the operating frequency from the 5 GHz band.

variables.name: GROUP_OWNER_INTENT_MIN
variables.comment:
* The least inclination to be a group owner, to be filled in the field
     * {@link #groupOwnerIntent}.

variables.name: GROUP_OWNER_INTENT_MAX
variables.comment:
* The most inclination to be a group owner, to be filled in the field
     * {@link #groupOwnerIntent}.

variables.name: GROUP_OWNER_INTENT_AUTO
variables.comment:
* The system can choose an appropriate owner intent value, to be filled in the field
     * {@link #groupOwnerIntent}.

variables.name: groupOwnerIntent
variables.comment:
* This is an integer value between {@link #GROUP_OWNER_INTENT_MIN} and
     * {@link #GROUP_OWNER_INTENT_MAX} where
     * {@link #GROUP_OWNER_INTENT_MIN} indicates the least inclination to be a group owner and
     * {@link #GROUP_OWNER_INTENT_MAX} indicates the highest inclination to be a group owner.
     *
     * A value of {@link #GROUP_OWNER_INTENT_AUTO} indicates the system can choose an appropriate
     * value.
     *
     * By default this field is set to {@link #GROUP_OWNER_INTENT_AUTO}.

methods.name: public String getNetworkName()
methods.comment: Get the network name of this P2P configuration, or null if unset.

methods.name: public String getPassphrase()
methods.comment: Get the passphrase of this P2P configuration, or null if unset.

methods.name: public int getGroupOwnerBand()
methods.comment:
* Get the required band for the group owner.
     * The result will be one of the following:
     * {@link #GROUP_OWNER_BAND_AUTO},
     * {@link #GROUP_OWNER_BAND_2GHZ},
     * {@link #GROUP_OWNER_BAND_5GHZ}

methods.name: public int getNetworkId()
methods.comment:
* Get the network ID of this P2P configuration.
     * @return either a non-negative network ID, or one of
     * {@link WifiP2pGroup#NETWORK_ID_PERSISTENT} or {@link WifiP2pGroup#NETWORK_ID_TEMPORARY}.

methods.name: public void writeToParcel(Parcel dest, int flags)
